Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.31,0:00:06.31,Default,,0,0,0,,STRIDER. Tells autonomous Marines what they are rolling onto.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.31,0:00:11.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Force Design 2030 puts Marines in places maps do not reach.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.32,0:00:16.32,Default,,0,0,0,,LOGCOM fields the autonomous tow tractor at MDMC Albany today, ALPV\Ntomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.33,0:00:21.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Forward rover snaps a frame. GOOSE off-road imagery, never leaves the\Nwire.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.85,0:00:23.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Fifty gigabytes of labelled terrain, on-prem.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.35,0:00:27.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Kamiwaza-deployed vision call: terrain frame becomes structured JSON.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.40,0:00:33.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Soft sand. Very-soft firmness. No water crossing.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.40,0:00:39.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Reasoner cross-references fording depth and ground clearance per\Nvehicle.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.40,0:00:45.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Green, amber, red. Binding constraint named in plain English.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.40,0:00:51.40,Default,,0,0,0,,ALPV caution. JLTV caution. ATT-EV NO-GO -- 6.5 inch clearance bogs in\Nsoft sand.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.43,0:00:55.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Convoy commander has the answer in four seconds.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.43,0:01:00.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Audit trail: full JSON every call. Operator can replay any decision.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.51,0:01:05.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Set KAMIWAZA_BASE_URL. Same code hits on-prem vLLM. 100% data\Ncontainment.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.52,0:01:10.52,Default,,0,0,0,,IL5 / IL6 ready. STIG-hardened. Inference Mesh handles the routing.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.52,0:01:15.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Built on the Kamiwaza Stack. Deploy in hours, not months.
